      "span_text": "This method of LG fitting is therefore practical for super-Gaussian and flat-top driven OAM beams whereas the method outlined in [CITATION_1] may be more useful for describing Gaussian driven OAM beams where accurate representation of power in the focal spot is of concern. Otherwise, we find the present method to be superior for describing the peak intensity and general shape of the OAM beam at focus."
